use the following requirement and rule when working on the assessment. Your assessment
will be scored based on the key indicators stated in Assessment Aspects section.

please make the UI is sensible or feel free to use existing UI Kit (bootstrap/foundation).

We suggest to focus on the working functionality and ensure the app is easy to use. You are free to add any assumption to ease your work.
